<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Http_Client_Adapter_Socket throws a notice for $this-&gt;config['sslusecontext'] on line 205.</p>

<p>config['sslusecontext'] is set in Http/Client/Adapter/Proxy.php to true, only if the secure flag is passed to connect(). It should be set to false, if the flag is not passed, so that no notice is thrown.</p>

